About:
Fly over 120 deepspace and Death Star surface missions against the Empire. Fly X-wings, Y-Wings and B-Wings. Full voice mission briefings with over 1000 spoken lines. Dogfighting, hi and run raids, treacherous escort missions.. all in the authentic Star Wars Galaxy. 
BONUS 14 missions from X-Wings VS TIE Fighter.Scattered resistance groups are uniting and what is needed most now are Starfighter pilots. Will you join their struggle to end this tyranny and become a hero of the Rebellion?
